replyTime":"2018-02-16T09:32:11.000Z","msg":"美國幫緊台灣去中華民國"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T10:09:58.000Z","msg":"你仲有面入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7151e13f663bdd81d0c30ddbe606bc916f21e245","tid":562730,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca5c697b3e10df4534416c0acdb7f1ba9b977af4","tid":562730,"uid":24140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c0f21adfe3249e56d67ca16f04e5ec8c95af20bd","tid":562730,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1a9482e4819ae7235a3e9a548924571db06ad667","tid":562730,"uid":23758,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T07:58:19.000Z","msg":"中華民國的確已經亡左國喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T09:15:01.000Z","msg":"根據舊金山和約<br />\n日本放棄台澎主權<br />\n台澎主權未定<br />\n另美對台六項保證<br />\n美不承認台澎主權屬於中國(國共)"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T09:32:11.000Z","msg":"美國幫緊台灣去中華民國"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T10:10:53.000Z","msg":"就算當年中(台)美聯防條約<br />\n美國無承認中華民國擁有台澎主權"},{"pid":"9e4df5f356754d10a0af1eef00ebd5b935a30c68","tid":562730,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T10:39:05.000Z","msg":"美國間接承認 Taiwan is not Republic of China<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee51aec21380201896d344f4cff419079ea2d3f1","tid":562730,"uid":71725,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T10:52:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}